BOB; LEGISLATION -- FLORIDA; ABORTION CLINICS; RIGHT TO LIFE; PRIVACY; WOMENS 
RIGHTS; PREGNANCY; MEDICAL ETHICS; GOVERNMENT REGULATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
