was found. ; Photo, Left, Eduardo Garcia Cacho with some of his wares; he has 
been dealing in looted artifactssince the 1950s. JAMES F. SMITH / Los Angeles 
Times; Map, Sipan, Peru 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
