thumbs-up on Wednesday after the Florida Legislature killed Gov. Bob Martinez' 
attempts to tighten restrictions on abortion. ; Photo, Rep. Barbara Boxer on 
Capitol Hill after abortion funding vote. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
