<TEXT>
<P>
No Excuses sportswear has given its latest No Excuses award to actress Zsa Zsa 
Gabor for her conviction for slapping a Beverly Hills cop -- "and taking her 
trial no more seriously than, 'Dahling, what a slap in the face.' " Zsa Zsa's 
