Ilona Staller, a member of the Italian Parliament, has called for a law 
creating guarded parking places for couples desiring intimacy in their cars. 
Staller, 38, a Hungarian-born porno star, made the proposal after a gunman 
attacked a couple parked on the outskirts of Genoa. 
</P>
<P>
A man in Boston was $1 million richer until police arrested him for allegedly 
running off with a bag of money that fell from an armored car onto a bridge. 
"He said he thought it was a bag of laundry," said police officer Paul Painten, 
who arrested the man about 100 yards from where the money fell. 
