<P>
CBS Inc.: The New York media firm said third-quarter net income dropped 11% to 
$61.8 million, while revenue rose 4% to $568 million. Despite the dip in 
profit, CBS said overall the firm continued to surpass its budgeted 
expectations, particularly the performance of the CBS Television Network. 
</P>
