to testify for the state as the lawsuit continues against the other 
defendants," Mattox said. 
</P>
<P>
The state is accusing the insurance industry of seeking to create a phony 
"insurance crisis" several years ago in which insurers claimed that an increase 
in lawsuits was forcing them out of the commercial liability field. 
