<P>
CHINA TOPS SAUDIS 2-1 IN SOCCER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times wire services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
SINGAPORE 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
North Korea and the United Arab Emirates fought to a scoreless tie, and China 
beat Saudi Arabia 2-1 tonight in the opening matches of the final Asian round 
for qualifying for the World Cup soccer tournament. 
</P>
</TEXT>
